General.Name: Audeara Ltd
General.Description: Audeara Limited, a hearing health technology company, engages in the development and sale of personalized listening products in Australia and North America. It provides A"01 and A-02 Bluetooth headphones; A-02 TV bundles; and BT"01 wireless transceivers. The company was incorporated in 2015 and is based in Fortitude Valley, Australia.
